equence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002438, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please) send blessings upon al-Hasan the son of Ali the son of Muhammad, the dutiful, the pious, the honest, the faithful, the shining light, the treasurer of Your knowledge, the reminder of the profession of Your Oneness, the authorized to undertake Your mission, the descendant of the leaders of the religion who are rightly guiding and rightly directing, and the argument against the inhabitants of this world. So, bless him, O my Lord, with the most favorite blessings that You have ever bestowed upon any of Your elite persons, argument-persons, and descendants of Your Messengers. O God of the worlds!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Hasan bin Ali bin Muhammad (a.s) par durood bhej jo khush kirdaar, parhez-gaar, saadiq, wafa-daar, chamakta huwa noor aur Tere uloom ke khazeene-daar hai. Woh Teri tawheed ka elaan karne waale, Tere hukm ke paas-daar, deen ke un Imaamo ke ja-nasheen keh jo rehbar aur raahe yaafta hai aur duniya waalo’n par Teri hujjat hai. Pas un par rehmat farma ay Parwardigaar behtareen rehmat jo Tu ne apne bar-guzido’n, apni hujjato’n aur apne nabiyyo’n ki aulaad mein se kisi par ki hai, ay jahano ke Ma’bood.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! حسنؑ ابن علیؑ ابن محمدؑ پر درود بھیج جو خوش کردار پرہیز گار صادق وفادار چمکتا ہوا نور اور تیرے علوم کے خزانہ دار ہیں وہ تیری توحید کا اعلان کرنے والے تیرے حکم کے پاسدار دین کے ان اماموں کے جانشین کہ جو رہبر اور راہ یافتہ ہیں اور دنیا والوں پر تیری حجت ہیں پس ان پر رحمت فرما اے پروردگار بہترین رحمت جو تو نے اپنے برگزیدوں اپنی حجتوں اور اپنے نبیوں کی اولاد میں سے کسی پر کی ہے اے جہانوں کے معبود۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAL HASANIB-NE A’LIYYIB-NE MOHAMMADE-NIL BARRIT TAQIY-YIS SAADE-QIL WA FEE-YIN NOO-RIL MOZEE-E KHAAZE-NE I’L-ME-KA WAL MOZAK-KERE BE-TAW-HEEDE-KA WA WALIYYE AMRE-KA WA KHALA-FE AIMMA-TID DEE-NIL HODAA-TIR RAA-SHE-DEENA WAL HUJJATE A’LAA AH-LID DUNYAA FA-SALLE A’LAIKA YAA RABBE AF-ZALA MAA SALLAIY-TA A’LAA AHA-DIN MIN AS-FEYAA-E-KA WA HOJA-JE-KA WA AWLAA-DE ROSOLE-KA YAA ILAA-HAL AA’LAMEE-NA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى الْحَسَنِ بْنِ عَلِيِّ بْنِ مُحَمَّدِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "الْبَرِّ التَّقِيِّ الصَّادِقِ الْوَفِيِّ النُّوْرِ الْمُضِيْءِ خَازِنِ عِلْمِكَ وَالْمُذَكِّرِ بِتَوْحِيْدِكَ وَ وَلِيِّ اَمْرِكَ وَخَلَفِ اَئِمَّةِ الدِّيْنَ الْهُدَاةِ الرَّاشِدِيْنَ وَالْحُجَّةِ عَلٰى اَهْلِ الدُّنْيَا فَصَلِّ عَلَيْهِ يَا رَبِّ اَفْضَلَ مَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلٰى اَحَدٍ مِّنْ اَصْفِيَائِكَ وَحُجَجِكَ وَاَوْلَادِ رُسُلِكَ يَا اِلٰهَ الْعَالَمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8":